data.description: ****15k towards Down Payment or Closing Cost using Preferred Lender if qualifications are met.****   Nestled in the prestigious Grove Park neighborhood, this meticulously renovated home offers luxurious living just steps away from Westside Reservoir Park and the future Microsoft Campus. This residence provides not only a home but also a lifestyle of unparalleled convenience and refinement. With four bedrooms and two bathrooms, this ranch boasts premium upgrades such as stainless steel appliances, granite counters, and hardwood floors.    The master suite is a private sanctuary, complete with a soaking tub, custom-tiled shower, and an oversized walk-in closet. Outside offer a private fenced backyard where you can unwind and rejuvenate. Experience convenience, refinement, and an unmatched location—your dream home awaits.
